Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:50.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会这样告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:53.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放任自己随波逐流
