Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  优  让你陪我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你至少要来参加一下晨练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  我叫黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来接我啊  谢谢真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢优
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有戴上它的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手环
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也替优做了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真透凑成一对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉看起来挺开朗的  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}「拼贴画」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把喜欢的材料按你喜欢的方式剪切后拼贴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游  你在干什么  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把剪刀交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她父母过来把她带回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕  真的好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真的疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本来就给人那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了别说了别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  心死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然打小篝  好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙耶老师对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小鸟游弄成那副样子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是提了下建议而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  痛苦只是一瞬间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受过痛苦的心灵会提高恢复力而再生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就再也不会受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的粉红色
