Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  心死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心  死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女生在哪里
