Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很讨厌咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多加牛奶进去就只是单纯的泥水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  咖啡在各方面比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想帮助小鸟游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚是不是要帮助她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想帮助她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去死就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  黑衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下美术室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到有趣的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在这里杀了她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是那么温柔的沙耶老师会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术室…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸟游同学的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话能把那幅画交给小鸟游同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在这里的话总觉得有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…是我让黄泉坏掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里都有点出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  经理人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优她没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也是经理人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经理人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部不是只有我一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  那个…优的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优？那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  但是合宿的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理经人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认人的记性不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有过那样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  她没事吧  黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她和一年级那个奇怪的人关系挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都会不知道优了  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼儿园的时候总是坐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处乱跑的优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学在海边教学的时候也是一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真透～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  不觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优的家也去玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我去玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救黄泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的时候我和你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的什么人和自己的烦恼进行战斗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是与我们完全没有关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是另一个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢  优
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个自己永远都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着我们的烦恼和混乱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在战斗中另一个自己最终死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些烦恼和感情才会最终消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有另一个自己带着烦恼死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才能从混乱迷惘的感情中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放弃最关注的事物之后变得自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个地方的另一个小鸟游如果死去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游就能从现在的烦恼中逃脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许小鸟游的烦恼的核心是真透  你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个世界的另一个自己如果死去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游就会把对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把对你的感情全部扼杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优所说的我一点都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼哪是谁死了  扼杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好对话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把双方的心意传达给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去依靠别人什么的  绝对太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把你当成我最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在遇到真透之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为真透倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  你想救小鸟游对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好对话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把双方的心意传达给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是依靠别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己来解决是很痛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我们为你承担的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直面伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那样的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救黄泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要救…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要救…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑岩射手…
